{{Quote|What about a hexenbesen?|Billy Maximoff|Darkest Hour / Wake Thy Power}}
[[Agatha Harkness' Coven]] woke up from their slumber to [[Lilia Calderu]]'s gasp. She had a vision and explained that the [[Salem Seven]] were coming. They ran away only to hear the commotion from all directions. Maximoff then stated his idea to use broomsticks, which everyone immediately hated, mostly because of the prejudice connotations that came with it. Upon hearing more noises, they agreed; however, not without a stern talking to by Calderu.
[[File:Billy Flying on Broom.png|{{AltFloat}}|Maximoff flying on his broom]]
